    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Long-handled spoons with a rounded bowl of a type patented in the late 19th century, designed for stirring sodas and ice cream floats that are served in tall glasses.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
